reviews.review_text: Easily my favorite McDonalds to go to. Fedelita and the rest of the team is so friendly - they always brighten my mornings! Thanks guys!

Surprisingly, the service at this McDonalds is very exceptional. It s very rare that a McDonalds can be so  outstanding. Anyway, if you want to eat some cheaper fast food, this particular store is definitely a recommend. Much better than the one in central Burnaby. Food : 5/5
The staff are well-attentive and greets us with glee! Makes the dining a whole Lot hearty.

I have only ever used the drive through here! And there is a reason for that...the one lady (wish I knew her name) is so lovely and kind. Always greets you with a smile! People like this deserve to get the spotlight of reviews! The line is always moving which is great and it is one of the better McDonalds in the area. Good quality food. Favorite stop now for my morning coffee!

E The staff here treat every customer as family they make you feel about welcome and important meal times here are extremely busy however they never miss a beat and the hustle and bustle doesnt effect how each is treated  best people here

Visiting this McDonalds twice so far, last time visiting was 6 months ago, and Ive found this is the best and the cleanest McDonalds I have ever visited. The staff are friendly. Food service is fast. The drink counter, table, chair, floor, and washroom are always clean. Very happy with this place.

My child loves McDonalds so we come here once or twice per month. We were having lunch here today (Jan 25 2023). The food was ok but i want to rate it 5 stars because it is very clean. There is a person here whose job is just to clean around. He is very good at his job, cleaning any litter, tables, garbage area etc. Then he moves discretely into some corner and watches around till the next table is free or he sees garbage somewhere. It is really nice to dine in here. It feels like you are a valuable guest and they take care of you.
Best McDonald s in the lower mainland, no exaggeration. Their jr chickens are always on point. 10/10.

Order the BLT chicken Sandwich from this location. It was better than my sad mcchicken sandwich.. My partner got the better sandwich, get that. Whom ever is on the grill for that sandwich tonight, great job. I ve lived in the area for years and that was my favourite bite from McDonald s.
I like their cheap no frills breakfasts.
Quick & fresh. Really nice lady at the drive thru in the mornings. (Currently missed!) (:
Good service food is always fresh and the staff are very considerate. 10/10 in the macdonalds category

I was not familiar with the area so it took me a minute before realizing where the drive through was. During my visit, it was so busy that I was so far from the drive through lane and I was on the road going into the parking lot. But despite during such busy hours, I only waited like 7-10 mins before it was my turn to order then 1 min before I pay and leave with my food. Minimal touching, nice service, and no hassle, nice.

Today I received excellent service, my kid dropped the soft drink, when I told about to one of the staff(middle-aged man) just smiled and cleaned it, he was so patient and best at service. Best experience!. Place also nice and good to dine with family.
Great drive thru/mobile pick up service in the mornings ! Lovely staff

I almost missed this McD. But, glad I saw it. It is small restaurant. All the same options as in any other McDs. I had an Angus burger with fries and coffee.  It is probably the most popular meal. It is tasty and juicy. The service was good. Good clean restaurant. I enjoyed my meal. This time I sat down after my order and a staff brought my meal.  That is a really good service. The guy keeping the place nice and tidy was quite friendly. I complimented on the good job he was doing. Lots of parking here.
Best McDonald s I ve been to. The staff is always so nice, with a great attitude. Great start to my day coming to this McDonald s :)

This is a great McDonalds, with Canadian tire across the street its convenient. The restaurant is clean, efficient, and well managed.  I recommend this location. The staff are helpful and keep the place clean.  Lots of parking, and easy to access.
Always fresh and consistent quality
Great service when we order create your own burger.  The staff (Meyelle) even remembered our drink and fries preferences. The Angus burger is juicy with a wide selection of toppings. Great value!
Very clean most of the time, also there are no homeless lingering around like some other locations, drive thru is sometimes very busy but they manage to move the car line ups quickly
Made a large order for my sons birthday. They were faster than anticipated and the order was hot and correct. Very friendly service and I would recommend!
I dont know why, but this place has better tasting food than other spots
Not chinsy. Filled my shamrock shake to the brim. Excellent experience.
I would recommend this location, your order is ready in a timely manor. The restaurant and washrooms are clean and the staff always have a smile and always friendly. 5 stars in my book
Great staff at the market crossing location in Burnaby. You can never go wrong with the classic cheeseburger and fries combination with the new summer special pineapple and coconut slushy.
Food was really good was little confused to why my cheese burger came in my fries box and the French fries where wrapped in my cheeseburger wrapper but other that then was good and friendly service.
Priyanka is the best manager ever. Amazing customer service skills. She deserves a raise!
It was actually very good. Sorry folks but I really think it is possible to have decent McDonalds food. I believe it is the crew chief / manager on duty who makes it good or bad.
Best staff ever! Super clean store. Food was fast and fresh
Alyssa was amazing she was very kind to my daughter and hosted a little coloring table for us. Nice location. Recommend this McDonald s!
All good
These are the hardest working people I think I ve ever seen. Fast and accurate too
Friendly. Good service. Self machines . They bring your food to the table! Almost best branch that I have ever been.
Friendly ppl....always happy to see me, especially Vatalia(hope I spelled right), coffee always good and not burned like other locations. Come through here twice a week :)
McDonalds at market crossing. By far my favourite McDonalds anywhere and the only one I rate above a 3.

A great place for a quick meal or coffee Very friendly staff from managers to front line counter personnel Always kept very clean including washrooms Lots of free parking Located in very convenient strip mall
When you try those new machines and enter your coupon. Get delivered in your booth. Get the extra smile. This is called impeccable service at mc and Im lovin it
Convenient pickup and to go fast food restaurant. Service is great. Love dropping by and getting some combos.

Staff are so personal they remember you and your order I go there every morning love them
Love the service here. Thats why I come back. There is one lady in the drive thru that just brightens my day
Fast service and I love that they use an order number system. Build your own burger machines are great too.
